{"tid":1359162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我地時間無多啦！！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-24T05:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T05:27:14.000Z","uid":43994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6a756f57090a1ed02ae19dd7270620d426bce778","tid":1359162,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:24:13.000Z","msg":"大家都知成個反送中運動，中學生大專生係一大主力<br />\n而家已經係7月尾，嚟緊8月中開始，有好多冇咁involved既大專生去咗Ocamp<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n9月之後，學生開學少咗好多時間，fg陸續開始返第一份工 <br />\n平日好似港鐵不合作運動 / 圍何妖議辦，依類活動會越來越少人參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好同我講咩罷學罷工，大家都知香港根本好難吹起三罷風潮<br />\n現實就係9月開始，我地既人數同政治能量會漸失<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔計727入元朗，9月之前我地只係得返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">5個週末</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間無多啦，大家計劃行動個時睇返個日曆<br />\n時刻提醒自己要做既主線任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好忘記我地6月以黎失去左啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>6位殉道烈士<br />\n過百名被捕義士<br />\n流亡台灣義士<br />\n被開槍爆頭毒打既抗爭者<br />\n無數個包括我你佢 被港共target左會拉既抗爭者</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n犧牲左咁多，我地換到啲咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>冇官員問責落台<br />\n冇警察為暴力鎖壓負責<br />\n冇全面撤回條例</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">係乜都冇呀</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得傘運失敗之後既抑鬱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得雨傘失敗之後，面對DQ、一地兩檢我地幾咁束手無策？<br />\n覆水難收，今次失敗之後，我地係會比5年前更慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">It is all or nothing</span></span><br />\n<br />\nAnyway 727元朗見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d298c4e68628ce940a4c73ef738b9828758eeb2b","tid":1359162,"uid":43994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}